title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Ryan Carter/Lavelle E. Neall III/Ron Johnson
description: Nordo is in for PA and baseball is back! At least for now, and we very excited about it. Fox Sports North's Ryan Carter joins to talk about the Wild. Lavelle E. Neal III in studio to talk the highly anticipated start to the MLB season. Fox 9's Ron Johnson in studio with the Gym Chronicles: The Naked Men Hordes and to talk some football.
